    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What Happens After Midnight is an action-survival horror FPS where you play as Lucy, a paranormal investigator sent to check out the small town of Nightvale. Things are not as they seem. The people are strange here and an ominous feeling grows as the clock gets closer to midnight. Then ensues a journey through other worlds to save our own.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore mysterious worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192490/extras/798017b604b737ec627c246f95b8e75c.poster.avif?t=1772385884\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192490/extras/798017b604b737ec627c246f95b8e75c.webm?t=1772385884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192490/extras/798017b604b737ec627c246f95b8e75c.mp4?t=1772385884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect resources and upgrades to get more powerful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192490/extras/71b389134b406c1e64f0f89908e7d98a.poster.avif?t=1772385884\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192490/extras/71b389134b406c1e64f0f89908e7d98a.webm?t=1772385884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192490/extras/71b389134b406c1e64f0f89908e7d98a.mp4?t=1772385884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight to survive against cosmic horrors and use immersive active reloads.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192490/extras/e29c1950b56f983428d52fdba1604903.poster.avif?t=1772385884\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192490/extras/e29c1950b56f983428d52fdba1604903.webm?t=1772385884\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192490/extras/e29c1950b56f983428d52fdba1604903.mp4?t=1772385884\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
